            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 2 poin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_4974664313555589786.png",
                "id": "talent20562",
                "key": "Steel Fang",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Steel Fang"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 3 poin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/5a7f4821eca7816e8d923684ccee651c_8602456918709239920.png",
                "id": "talent81588",
                "key": "Claw and Thunder",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Claw and Thunder"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 3 poin </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">. Karakter ini memperoleh status </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The Wolf Within</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">The Wolf Within</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Setelah Karakter yang terpengaruh menggunakan Normal Attack atau Elemental Skill</span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Mengakibatkan 2</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">poin</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/898eb03f9942b7b7833a3c082a86fdef_2263727005267873706.png",
                "id": "talent38710",
                "key": "Lightning Fang",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lightning Fang"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Electro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_1283673223482953.png",
                "id": "talent17089",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1780433756009620278.png",
